familyLongDescrptionVal" value="Looking for a women's pirate costume that is completely <i>you</i>-nique? Then it's time to check out our pirate costume accessories! 
<p>Let your imagination set sail and create your own original pirate costume. We have a variety of mix-and-match accessories to create a head-to-toe pirate costume. Our deluxe pirate hat will have you ready to lead the crew on a hunt for buried treasure. Next you need a women's pirate jacket to set yourself apart from the rest of the scalawags and show them who is running this ship. Now that you have the essentials, put on your pirate boots and you're ready to make them walk the plank in your one-of-a-kind pirate costume. Choose from our pirate eye patch, boot covers, and more to accessorize your <i>arrgh</i>-guably adorable pirate captain look.</p>
<p>With all of these options, you're sure to create a pirate costume that fits your personality. Mix and match our captain costume accessories to create new and unique pirate costume ideas! </p>
<p>Browse our Create Your Own Women's High Seas Pirate Costume accessories to complement the pirate costume you already have, or shop the whole set! </p>">
